 x
Cx^2 - 2Bx + 2A \geq  0\to \frac1c(x^2-\frac{2B}{c}x+\frac{2A}{C})= \frac1c((x-\frac{B}{C})^2-\frac{B^2}{c^2}+\frac{2A}{c})\ge0\to
\frac1c(x-\frac{B}{C})^2-\frac{B^2}{c}+\frac{2A}{1}\ge0\to -\frac{B^2}{c}+\frac{2A}{1}\ge0\to B^2 \leq 2AC
